<div class="wprm-recipe-template-copy-of-tracys-cutout-template-container">
	<div class="wprm-recipe-template-copy-of-tracys-cutout-template-header">
		<h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Braised Beef and Radish</h2>
		<div class="wprm-spacer" style="height: 5px;"></div>
		<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">Delicious Asian Chinese flavor beef stew with radish is one of my comfort foods. This Cantonese style Chinese braised beef brisket and daikon instant pot recipe takes around 2 hours.&nbsp;</span></div>
