		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>I just cooked this dish today.</p>
<p>I use beef hind muscles (shin/shank) - after braising - it so buttery smooth compared to othe cuts</p>
<p>For the sauce, I use:<br />
Chu Hou paste, oyster sauce, dark soya sauce and light soya sauce</p>
<p>Also added :<br />
Bay leaves and dried orange peel </p>
<p>Rest opf the ingregrtedients as per what the author used - ginger,garlic, onions, sugar etc</p>
		</div>

		<div class="comment-reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-2750" data-commentid="2750" data-postid="5841" data-belowelement="article-comment-2750" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Yong" aria-label="Reply to Yong">Reply</a></div>
		
